episodes.title: Youth Is the Season of Hope
episodes.plot: The Cuthberts' boarders stir excitement with a question: Could there be gold in Avonlea? Elsewhere, Gilbert makes a new friend at sea.

episodes.title: Signs Are Small Measurable Things, But Interpretations Are Illimitable
episodes.plot: The steamer lands in Trinidad, bringing Bash face to face with his past. The Barrys get behind the gold rush, but Matthew and Marilla aren't so sure.

episodes.title: The True Seeing Is Within
episodes.plot: An adventure away with the Barrys teaches Anne to trust her instincts. Marilla begins to suspect that her boarders aren't as innocent as they seem.

episodes.title: The Painful Eagerness of Unfed Hope
episodes.plot: Anne writes letters as an "agent of romance" while Diana trains at home to be a lady. A life-changing encounter steers Gilbert toward his destiny.

episodes.title: The Determining Acts of Her Life
episodes.plot: A game of spin the bottle prompts burning questions about love and beauty. Anne and Cole bond over their differences as Gilbert makes his way home.

episodes.title: I Protest Against Any Absolute Conclusion
episodes.plot: Anne faces the world with a shocking new look while the town preps for its annual Christmas pantomime. Gilbert and Bash join the Cuthberts for dinner.

episodes.title: Memory Has as Many Moods as the Temper
episodes.plot: Cole accompanies the girls to Aunt Josephine's for a lavish party filled with surprises. Back at home, Marilla's health takes a worrisome turn.

episodes.title: Struggling Against the Perception of Facts
episodes.plot: With a wedding on the horizon, Anne wonders what kind of bride she'd like to be. Marilla sees an oculist, and Bash meets a friendly face in "The Bog".

episodes.title: What We Have Been Makes Us What We Are
episodes.plot: A brand-new teacher brings unconventional methods -- and a motorbike -- to Avonlea. Gilbert's plan to speed up his studies leaves Bash feeling lost.

episodes.title: The Growing Good of the World
episodes.plot: Anne rallies her friends to save Miss Stacy in the wake of a disastrous incident. Bash gets an unexpected gift, and Cole makes a surprising choice.
